{"tid":2462344,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"有冇手足依家會好似我咁做？","createTime":"2021-03-26T03:07:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T05:28:36.000Z","uid":14090,"like":11,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"606a9356267535465e9834ce51289be47bd5ab16","tid":2462344,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T03:07:14.000Z","msg":"驚入到去唔習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家日日食到勁清 跟住入面個餐單食<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又勁早起身 鬧鐘聲cap咗同囚啲對話 嚇到自己醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用凍水沖涼 因為入面隨時冇熱水<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n放一兩隻虱落張床 等自己皮膚習慣下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n買咗啲質地勁差既衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n準時一個鐘放風<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n禁慾<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋瘋狂睇月黑高飛 以備不時之需<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8afb5c8da33d53719d0953186427159a9697c81","tid":2462344,"uid":335303,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T03:08:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3584498e235fcad1019d095c54664991dd3e3e9d","tid":2462344,"uid":14090,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T03:09:17.000Z","msg":"唉屌 好sad"},{"pid":"cc641a92d39222fc179056aea6560ed01cda06ed","tid":2462344,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T03:13:11.000Z","msg":"有冇手足一齊體驗下"},{"pid":"6f346b743368ca1d15ffcaaee9df515eeb384593","tid":2462344,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"re